name: The destruction of a Hitler
description:
The ideological strengths that he built and the military status made him fill a full role in the tribal defense of dominating life in all elements, which made me so disgusted with why his constructs didn't improve, and it certainly reflected on understanding in his mind which shattered him in and his military enrichment.

The real revolution intended for life's diversity is, not war, but our role as humans who know the true purpose of life as one and the mind of life together.
